<h1>Become a Mentor!</h1>

<p>
  Mentors are the keystone of our programs. Mentors engage and inspire students
  in ways far beyond science and technology. They enable both students and
  adults to appreciate the value of sportsmanship, teamwork, and Gracious
  Professionalism<sup>®</sup>.

</p>

<p>
  An <strong>FTC Coach/Mentor</strong> works with his or her students by helping
  them to develop skills and to design and build a successful robot. They guide
  teams through any issues they encounter, making them stronger in both their
  school and personal lives.
</p>

