<p>
  <strong>FRC Mentors</strong> play a vital role in the success of their
  students. Mentors work extensively with team members during the build season,
  designing, building, and fabricating a functional robot for Competition. Their
  expertise is the catalyst for the team’s and students’ success. FRC Mentors
  are the major distinction between the FRC program and other robotic
  competitions as they are wholly the professional role model for the student.
</p>

